definition: something bought, i.e. property, but only livestock; abstractly, acquisition
kjvTranslation: cattle, flock, herd, possession, purchase, substance.

translations.bg: нещо купено, т.е. собственост, но само добитък; абстрактно - придобиване

translations.da: noget købt, dvs. ejendom, men kun husdyr; abstrakt set, erhvervelse
translations.de: etwas Gekauftes, d.h. Eigentum, aber nur Vieh; abstrakt, Erwerb

translations.fi: jotain ostettua eli omaisuutta, mutta vain karjaa; abstraktisti hankintaa
